{"lemma":"عَسَلٌ","slug":"عَسَلٌ","root":"ع.س.ل","root_slug":"ع-س-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-س-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عَسَل","root":"عسل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n29119"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to move, to vibrate, to shake","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to admix with honey","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to feed honey"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to produce honey (of bees)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to admix with honey","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be as sweet as honey"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to sleep lightly, to nap"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to feed and supply honey","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"honey","tags":["uncountable"],"examples":[{"text":"وَأَنْهَارٌ مِنْ عَسَلٍ مُصَفًّى"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n29119","headword_ar":"عَسَلٌ","root":"Esl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Honey;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fluid that is discharged from the mouths of bees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when they have eaten, of the flowers and the leaves, what fills their bellies, these substances being then converted by God, within their bellies, into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Easal","text_ar":"عَسَل"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which they eject from their mouths:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA: [in which, and in the K, several other explanations are added, too fanciful to deserve notice:]) the word is mase. and fem.; (S, O, Msb, K;) in most instances fem.: (S, O, Msb:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EasalapN","text_ar":"عَسَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"somewhat, thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, O, TA;) being the n. un.: (TA:) the dim. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EusayolapN","text_ar":"عُسَيْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", because"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EasalN","text_ar":"عَسَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is mostly fem., or as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EasalapN","text_ar":"عَسَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, Msb;) or it is the dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EasalapN","text_ar":"عَسَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EasalN","text_ar":"عَسَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEosaAlN","text_ar":"اَعْسَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of pauc.] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EusulN","text_ar":"عُسُلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EusolN","text_ar":"عُسْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EusuwlN","text_ar":"عُسُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EusolaAnN","text_ar":"عُسْلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (AHn, K;) and these pls. are used when one means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sorts of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Easal","text_ar":"عَسَل"},{"kind":"text","text":". (AHn, TA.) ―         -b2-  [It is also used tropically for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naworN","text_ar":"نَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Flowers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blossoms;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because honey is made therefrom. (See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarasa","text_ar":"جَرَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  And it is applied also to (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sweet, thick, inspissated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"melligenous, juice"},{"kind":"text","text":"of fruit:] and it signifies [particularly] (assumed tropical:)  the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"juice that flows from fresh ripe dates;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, * TA;) because of its sweetness. (O.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dibosN","text_ar":"دِبْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-  Also (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gum of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"species of mimosa called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurofuT","text_ar":"عُرْفُط"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]; (O, K;) because of its sweetness. (O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Easalu All~ubonaY","text_ar":"عَسَلُ اللُّبْنَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"is (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The gum that flows from the species of tree called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~ubonaY","text_ar":"اللُّبْنَى"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having no sweetness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"substance"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (M, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain odoriferous substance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that exudes from the species of tree above mentioned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, * TA,) i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmayoEapu","text_ar":"المَيْعَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[generally applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"storax,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"styrax"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lbn","text_ar":"لبن"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used for fumigation, and called by the vulgar"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSaY lubaAnK","text_ar":"حَصَى لُبَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K. [See art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HSw","text_ar":"حصو"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HSY","text_ar":"حصى"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Easalu Alr~imovi","text_ar":"عَسَلُ الرِّمْثِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A white thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"substance, a species of manna,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that comes forth from the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shrub called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rimov","text_ar":"رِمْث"},{"kind":"text","text":", [q. v.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumaAn","text_ar":"جُمَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pearls,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"silver beads like pearls"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, * TA.) ―         -b5-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"righteous, deed, the eulogy for which is deemed sweet."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, O.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAsilN","text_ar":"عَاسِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  And The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabaAb","text_ar":"حَبَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ripples"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of running water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O, K,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arising"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the blowing of the wind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O.) ―         -b2-  [In one place in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEasalu","text_ar":"العَسَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEasolu","text_ar":"العَسْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EanosalN","text_ar":"عَنْسَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.]"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","O","Msb","Mgh","M","IAar"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}